query:
-- Verificar leads que se tornaram personais (mesmo email)
SELECT 
  qr.leadEmail as lead_email,
  qr.leadName as lead_name,
  qr.createdAt as lead_date,
  u.email as user_email,
  u.name as user_name,
  u.createdAt as user_date,
  p.id as personal_id,
  p.subscriptionStatus
FROM quiz_responses qr
LEFT JOIN users u ON LOWER(qr.leadEmail) = LOWER(u.email)
LEFT JOIN personals p ON u.id = p.userId
WHERE qr.leadEmail IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY qr.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 20;
